title: Gone With The Blastwave - Ep1 - 66

Web comic by Kimmo Lemetti started in February 2, 2005

Gone With the Blastwave is about 2 Red Army soldiers wandering about in the huge, unhabited, war-torn city of New Porvoo. After a nuclear war that has destroyed most of the Earth. The only thing left to do is to fight and kill the enemy soldiers, from the Yellow and the Blue army, by any means necessary
